#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:247
msgid "Enable output"
msgstr "出力を有効化"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:251
msgid "Show Last Updated date on enabled post types."
msgstr "有効な投稿タイプに最終更新日を表示します。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:256
msgid "Automatic placement"
msgstr "自動配置"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:259
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:371
msgid "After content"
msgstr "コンテンツの後に"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:260
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:372
msgid "Before content"
msgstr "コンテンツの前に"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:261
msgid "Before and after content"
msgstr "コンテンツの前後に"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:262
msgid "Manual only (template tag)"
msgstr "手動のみ（テンプレートタグ）"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:264
msgid ""
"Use Manual to place output via the template tag in your theme. See the Usage "
"tab for examples."
msgstr ""
"手動のみを使用して、テーマ内でテンプレートタグ経由で出力を配置します。例につ"
"いては「使用とサポート」タブをご覧ください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:268
msgid "Label template"
msgstr "ラベルテンプレート"

#. translators: 1: literal %s token shown as code, 2: example label shown as code
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:275
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Use %1$s where the date should appear, e.g. %2$s. Omit %1$s to show the "
"label with no date."
msgstr ""
"日付を表示する場所に%1$sを使用してください（例：%2$s）。日付なしのラベルを表"
"示する場合は%1$sを省略してください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:284
msgid "Date format source"
msgstr "日付フォーマットのソース"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:287
msgid "Use WordPress site date format"
msgstr "WordPressサイトの日付フォーマットを使用"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:288
msgid "Use custom date format"
msgstr "カスタム日付フォーマットを使用"

#. translators: %s is a URL
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:294
#, php-format
msgid "Custom format uses PHP date format tokens. %s"
msgstr ""
"カスタム形式はWordPressで使用されるPHP日付フォーマットトークンを使用します。"
"%s"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:295
msgid "Format reference"
msgstr "フォーマットリファレンス"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:302
msgid "Custom date format"
msgstr "カスタム日付フォーマット"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:305
msgid "Only used when Date format source is set to Custom. Default: F j, Y"
msgstr ""
"日付フォーマットのソースがカスタムに設定されている場合のみ使用。デフォルト: "
"F j, Y"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:309
msgid "Visibility condition"
msgstr "表示条件"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:313
msgid "Only show when modified date differs from publish date."
msgstr "更新日を公開日と異なる場合のみ表示します。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:318
msgid "Post type mode"
msgstr "投稿タイプモード"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:321
msgid "Show only on selected post types"
msgstr "選択した投稿タイプのみ表示"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:322
msgid "Show on all public post types except selected"
msgstr "選択したものを除くすべての公開投稿タイプに表示"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:327
msgid "Post types"
msgstr "投稿タイプ"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:352
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "設定を保存"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:361
msgid "Automatic Injection"
msgstr "自動挿入"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:362
msgid ""
"When a placement mode other than Manual is selected, the plugin "
"automatically injects the last-updated label into singular post/page content "
"via the_content filter."
msgstr ""
"手動以外配置モードが選択されると、プラグインはthe_contentフィルター経由で"
"singular投稿/ページコンテンツに最終更新ラベルを自動挿入します。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:366
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "モード"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:367
msgid "Expected output position"
msgstr " 예상される出力位置"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:371
msgid "Label appears below the post body."
msgstr "ラベルは投稿本文の下に表示されます。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:372
msgid "Label appears above the post body."
msgstr "ラベルは投稿本文の上に表示されます。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:373
msgid "Before and after"
msgstr "前後"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:373
msgid "Label appears both above and below the post body."
msgstr "ラベルは投稿本文の上下両方に表示されます。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:374
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:461
msgid "Manual only"
msgstr "手動のみ"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:374
msgid ""
"Nothing is injected automatically. Use the template tag below in your theme "
"file."
msgstr ""
"何も自動挿入されません。テーマファイルの下のテンプレートタグを使用してくださ"
"い。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:378
msgid "Label Template"
msgstr "ラベルテンプレート"

#. translators: %s is a literal %s token placeholder shown in code
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:383
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The Label template setting controls the text displayed. Use %s as the date "
"placeholder."
msgstr ""
"ラベルテンプレート設定はdisplayされるテキストを制御します。日付のプレースホル"
"ダーとして%sを使用してください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:391
msgid "Template setting"
msgstr "テンプレート設定"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:392
msgid "Example frontend output"
msgstr "フロントエンド出力の例"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:396
msgid "Updated March 28, 2026"
msgstr "2026年3月28日に更新"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:397
msgid "Last checked: March 28, 2026"
msgstr "最終確認: 2026年3月28日"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:398
msgid "Fresh content  (no date appended — displayed as-is)"
msgstr "新鮮なコンテンツ（日付なし — そのまま表示）"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:402
msgid "Template Tags"
msgstr "テンプレートタグ"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:403
msgid ""
"Use these PHP functions anywhere in your theme when placement is set to "
"Manual."
msgstr ""
"配置が手動に設定されている場合、テーマ内のどこにでもこれらのPHP関数を使用でき"
"ます。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:406
msgid ""
"Echoes the rendered HTML directly. Use inside The Loop or pass a post ID."
msgstr ""
"レンダリングされたHTMLを直接エコーします。Loop内または投稿IDを渡して使用して"
"ください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:409
msgid "Expected HTML output:"
msgstr "预期されるHTML出力："

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:413
msgid ""
"Returns the rendered HTML string instead of echoing. Useful for further "
"manipulation."
msgstr ""
"エコーする代わりにレンダリングされたHTML文字列を返します。さらなる操作に便利"
"です。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:417
msgid "Date Format Reference"
msgstr "日付フォーマットリファレンス"

#. translators: %s is a URL
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:422
#, php-format
msgid ""
"When using a custom date format, the same PHP date tokens used by WordPress "
"apply. %s"
msgstr ""
"カスタム日付フォーマットを使用する場合、WordPressで使用される同じPHP日付トー"
"クンが適用されます。%s"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:423
msgid "View full format reference &rarr;"
msgstr "完全なフォーマットリファレンスを見る &rarr;"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:428
msgid "Token"
msgstr "トークン"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:428
msgid "Example output"
msgstr "出力例"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:430
msgid "March 28, 2026"
msgstr "2026年3月28日"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:431
msgid "28/03/2026"
msgstr "2026/03/28"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:432
msgid "2026-03-28"
msgstr "2026-03-28"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:433
msgid "28 Mar 2026"
msgstr "2026年3月28日"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:437
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "よくある質問"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:439
msgid "The label is not appearing on my posts."
msgstr "ラベルが投稿に表示されません。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:441
msgid "Check that Enable output is ticked on the Settings tab."
msgstr "設定タブで出力を有効화가チェックされていることを確認してください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:442
msgid ""
"Check that the post type (e.g. Post, Page) is selected in the Post types "
"list."
msgstr ""
"投稿タイプリストで投稿タイプ（例：投稿、固定ページ）が選択されていることを確"
"認してください。"

#. translators: %s is a setting name
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:447
#, php-format
msgid ""
"If %s is ticked, the label will only show when the article has been edited "
"after its original publish date."
msgstr ""
"%sがチェックされている場合、ラベルは記事が元の公開日後に編集されたときのみ表"
"示されます。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:448
msgid "Only show when modified date differs from publish date"
msgstr "更新日を公開日と異なる場合のみ表示"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:452
msgid ""
"If Automatic placement is set to Manual, nothing is injected automatically — "
"add the template tag to your theme."
msgstr ""
"自動配置が手に設定されている場合、何も自動挿入されません — テーマテンプレート"
"タグを追加してください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:455
msgid "How do I place the label exactly where I want it?"
msgstr "ラベルを好きな場所に配置するにはどうすればいいですか？"

#. translators: %1$s and %2$s are setting/function names
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:460
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Set Automatic placement to %1$s on the Settings tab, then add %2$s in your "
"theme template wherever you want it to appear."
msgstr ""
"設定タブで自動配置を%1$sに設定し、ラベルを表示したいテーマテンプレートの場所"
"に%2$sを追加してください。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:467
msgid "Can I show just a static label with no date?"
msgstr "日付なしの静的なラベルのみを表示できますか？"

#. translators: %s is a literal %s placeholder shown in code
#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:472
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Remove %s from the Label template. The text will be output as-is with "
"no date appended."
msgstr ""
"はい。ラベルテンプレートから%sを削除してください。テキストはそのまま出力さ"
"れ、日付は追加されません。"

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:479
msgid ""
"If you need help with setup, have found a bug, or want to request a feature, "
"get in touch."
msgstr ""
"設定のヘルプが必要であれば、バグを見つけた場合、または機能をリクエストしたい"
"場合は、お問い合わせください。"

